ORIGINAL WORK ATTRIBUTION:
This T.018 2nd generation implementation maintains the same educational
and training objectives as the T.001 1st generation project.

Both projects serve the ADRASEC community for emergency response
training and COSPAS-SARSAT protocol validation.

